Beth,<br><br>
Just being there and trusting him will mean more than you can imagine.  It will always be difficult.  I have tried my wifes patience almost daily.  Almost 32 years of putting up with a guy whos is moody and likes to islolate himself in a corner of the house away from everyone else.  She has always been there when I needed her, but she has never treated me with kid gloves.<br><br>
I always know even when the air is blue with the stress I can cause that times will be perfect soemtime later.  Many will not tolerate this and others just don't care.<br><br>
The fact that you care will keep him around.  He needs that desparately.  I am sure of that.<br><br>
Peace and Good Luck
